Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.79,0:00:06.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.10,0:00:09.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to know more about what happened in Vladivostok?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:13.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The body of an MI6 agent,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.05,0:00:15.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,the involvement of the CIA,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:20.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,and the illegal Japanese intelligence agency that's rumored to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:24.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, you know that better than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.05,0:00:30.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,From the way you talk, you seem to know why BK201's star disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.65,0:00:31.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.78,0:00:36.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I heard some dangerous anti-contractor weapon was used.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.63,0:00:38.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,An anti-contractor weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.29,0:00:42.30,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,As the name implies, it's a weapon that can take out contractors.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.30,0:00:46.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you have seen something similar to the prototype two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.56,0:00:51.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.55,0:00:54.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard about the Mitaka document?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:01:02.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The thing you're looking for, that mysterious document, is in the hands of a certain organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:04.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The key word is "Izanami."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.62,0:01:08.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! How do you know what I'm looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.28,0:01:09.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What is the Mitaka document?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.87,0:01:11.30,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Make a wish upon a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.35,0:01:17.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Upon a tiny, little, red star.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.57,0:01:22.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,"May I meet BK201 again."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.25,0:01:27.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Red star...
