Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:16.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The projectile is off by 2 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.15,0:03:21.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's a pretty good shot from this distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:23.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There are three rounds left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:28.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean you can only use this monster three more times?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:33.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No, each time it manifests, I have one round in the chamber and five in my pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.08,0:03:40.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that I have to maintain it since the warping and scratches don't disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:45.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty enthusiastic about this, young miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:48.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:52.75,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Go eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.43,0:04:00.14,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to pass on lunch and save money again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:02.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I won't eat anything strange again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.73,0:04:04.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:08.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I need to become stronger before I run away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.67,0:04:14.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And in order to realize that, I have to overcome my dislikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:19.44,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Something proper, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.83,0:04:23.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What do contractors eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:25.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Raw meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:27.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that from your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.06,0:04:28.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.23,0:04:29.44,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Me being a contractor...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:34.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I could tell without asking him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:39.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Michiru-san was a contractor too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:41.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Michiru-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:48.30,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:52.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I had the right to board Noah's Ark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:55.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,My parents nagged me on that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:59.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought it wouldn't be a bad experience to see the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:03.27,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She was good at making sweets. She was a normal housewife.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:06.21,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it happened when Norio was three.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.21,0:05:09.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She became a contractor, and by the time her personality started to deteriorate,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:11.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,she was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:14.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where she is and what she's doing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:19.24,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:24.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tasty?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:25.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:26.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Have as much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:28.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The liver creates blood, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.71,0:05:30.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Especially now that you are—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.31,0:05:31.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:35.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you {\i1}that{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:43.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,My star is cryin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.46,0:05:50.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I, who hath been born beneath the scorching and passionate star, have to finally remunerate...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:52.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,with my love for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.07,0:05:57.45,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:06:00.54,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hold on! Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:08.51,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you know? My mommy's a contractor!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:09.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:14.01,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Our meeting must be destiny at work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.01,0:06:16.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Your love for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:18.77,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you know about me anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:20.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me all about yourself, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.37,0:06:21.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,As I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:27.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You sparkle brighter than the fake stars in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:37.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's board Noah's Ark together!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:40.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Give her a mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:43.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about the reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:45.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She'll only slow me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:49.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She has a better aim with a rifle than I have, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:50.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,that's really all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.33,0:06:53.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I can do that mission alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:13.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.13,0:07:18.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Lebanon gave me an earthenware pot and gas burner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.07,0:07:18.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Earthenware pot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:21.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She really is impulsive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.38,0:07:25.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,When she opened it, there was a cockroach inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:31.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Then "bang"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:33.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:36.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Because I hate bugs now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.57,0:07:41.21,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to hit me again, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:44.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:45.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.78,0:07:47.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But in exchange, hit me on the left side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:48.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:51.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The right side is still hurting from the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.94,0:07:55.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to move properly if there's no balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:59.24,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.24,0:08:01.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're so irritating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.41,0:08:11.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you'll freeze to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:14.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A cockroach, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:17.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It must be because of her friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:23.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Even though she's used to her new powers, what happened to her friend must really have shocked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:25.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She was saying things about love and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:28.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She was really worried about her friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:32.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt there's anyone she likes though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:37.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:41.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm the same as a cockroach, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:49.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Guess this is the warmest room here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:52.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.91,0:08:57.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Even though she's a contractor, there's no pattern in her behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:09:00.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't lose interest in her hobbies, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:03.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There were too many things she didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:07.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps she wasn't really what you'd call an adult human.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:10.56,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And then she became a contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.56,0:09:13.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A contractor who's accumulating social experiences...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:15.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:19.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She's probably accumulating more experience to help her make logical decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:25.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She's still a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.61,0:09:28.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:39.40,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The Mitaka document... Izanami...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.40,0:09:41.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I believing her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:43.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But that's the only clue I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.64,0:09:50.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ichinose-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:52.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Kobayashi is calling for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:56.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You've got new orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:10:01.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We want you to transport an important object from a facility in Sapporo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:04.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Codename: Izanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:09.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to chase after BK201.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:12.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Or are you saying there's more behind this order?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:17.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course there is a reason we can't be careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.29,0:10:20.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We've been informed by our agent in Sapporo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.48,0:10:25.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He spotted BK201 in the company of some kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.09,0:10:30.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He's in Sapporo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:33.04,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(371,701)}Episode 5\NThe gunpowder is drifting away, so is the life...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:39.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,At least knock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:41.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:45.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Pursuers?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.61,0:10:46.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How many?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:49.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Three. One of them is a contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:54.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll draw their attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:58.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You three escape through the entrance while they're distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.85,0:11:01.21,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll regroup at the usual place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:31.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:15.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,BK201 was living here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.32,0:12:17.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, with a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:20.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Girl? Not a boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:22.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Unless he was cross-dressing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:29.44,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,According to the family register, Shion Pavlichenko had a twin sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.44,0:12:32.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But we know nothing about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:35.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She might have been killed by the FSB.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.97,0:12:42.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If the person with BK201 is truly a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:44.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:46.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.31,0:12:49.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The people at the research lab are awaiting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.74,0:13:03.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It smells great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:09.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,According to dad, it's around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:16.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:20.27,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:22.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.73,0:13:23.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:24.74,DTB-Overlap,,0,0,0,,Should I kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.19,0:13:26.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.21,0:13:30.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think he will cause any problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:33.00,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:44.51,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They're too careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:56.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll practice sniping.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:14:00.40,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is that the first thing you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:03.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:07.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Without lying to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:10.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand why I should kill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:12.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I can't shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.25,0:14:17.01,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,As long as it moves... it doesn't have to be a living target, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.01,0:14:18.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand the reason, so—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.76,0:14:21.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There is a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:25.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,To eliminate your irregularities as a contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.84,0:15:22.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:26.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:31.24,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:33.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I saw her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:35.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It was her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.46,0:15:36.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That was mom—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:40.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You took the flowers in the bathroom, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:44.24,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:48.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! We're in the middle of an important family discu—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:53.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let me use your oven.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.61,0:15:57.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know who BK201's client is,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.57,0:16:01.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,but it's certain they hid him here to target the goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:04.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, we would have transported it by air,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:08.00,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,but BK201 gets close to his target by blending into the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:10.14,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There are too many people at the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.14,0:16:11.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll transport it by water this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:13.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, that's no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.58,0:16:15.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We should just get it over with already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:19.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Says the bum who got his ass kicked by that little kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.88,0:16:21.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That really hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:26.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll check the Izanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:48.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The security is really tight in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:50.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:55.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wish upon a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:57.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:16:58.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.36,0:17:06.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be long before our wish and her wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.66,0:17:22.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:25.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Izanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:48.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.74,0:17:50.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,These are weeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:52.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They're edible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:56.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,My dad taught me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:17:59.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:05.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I shot a hole in the hotel's wall and made us stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:06.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:11.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She's trying to apologize?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.17,0:18:23.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.96,0:18:28.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,As long as it's nutritious, it doesn't matter how it tastes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:34.21,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So it tastes so bad you have to think the taste doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.02,0:18:44.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Refill.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:18:59.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:01.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:05.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps a bit hard for a first mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.24,0:19:08.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.36,0:19:11.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If you pay me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.87,0:19:13.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A reward?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:17.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you spoiling your handyman?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.95,0:19:20.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm paying her in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:25.30,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,As a contractor, you take on missions and get paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:27.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:30.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I can definitely do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.39,0:19:37.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This is a terrible night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:43.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A ship from Section 3 will enter the harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:49.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If I can destroy the goods before it arrives in the harbor, there won't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:50.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If I fail...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:55.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,you'll shoot when they're unloading the goods from the trucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:58.05,DTB-Overlap,,0,0,0,,...it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:20:01.05,DTB-Overlap,,0,0,0,,...Izanami... the trucks...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.40,0:21:17.90,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Kureteku yuubae ni senaka osarete
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.40,0:21:17.90,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}My back is pressed by the darkening glow of dusk
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.06,0:21:28.41,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Arukidasu kage ga shimesu hou e
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.06,0:21:28.41,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I start walking toward where my shadow points
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.41,0:21:37.97,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Taenai ikutsu mo no deai to wakare o
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.41,0:21:37.97,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Repeating the many, ceaseless encounters and partings
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.10,0:21:44.15,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Kurikaeshi doko e mukau no ka
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.10,0:21:44.15,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Where do I head to?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.90,0:21:49.25,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Hito wa dare mo mayoinagara
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.90,0:21:49.25,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}For all people, while they are lost,
Dialogue: 2,0:21:48.88,0:21:54.01,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}tsumi to iu na no sadame o seotte
Dialogue: 2,0:21:48.88,0:21:54.01,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}they bear the fate known as sin
Dialogue: 3,0:21:53.78,0:22:02.66,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Sore de mo nao ikiru imi o shiru darou
Dialogue: 3,0:21:53.78,0:22:02.66,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Nevertheless, I'll still learn of the meaning to live, right?
Dialogue: 4,0:22:02.48,0:22:07.75,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Bokura wa sou Day by Day
Dialogue: 4,0:22:02.48,0:22:07.75,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}That's right, Day by Day,
Dialogue: 5,0:22:07.49,0:22:14.70,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ashita e tsuzuku michi no tochuu de
Dialogue: 5,0:22:07.49,0:22:14.70,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}we're midway on the road leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 6,0:22:14.33,0:22:22.29,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Now Say It Again kimi to futari no mama
Dialogue: 6,0:22:14.33,0:22:22.29,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Now Say It Again, though it'd be great if
Dialogue: 7,0:22:22.21,0:22:32.58,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}irareta nara ii no ni naa...
Dialogue: 7,0:22:22.21,0:22:32.58,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I could remain together with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.19,0:22:38.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I saw a whale, but I didn't take a picture of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.68,0:22:41.00,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.58,0:22:43.00,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.78,0:22:47.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think of it, I should have taken a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.77,0:22:49.83,DTB-Overlap,,0,0,0,,Woah! It's so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.83,0:22:51.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is that a whale?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:54.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No! Whales are much bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.26,0:22:58.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And they spurt salt water!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.02,0:22:59.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Salt water?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.06,0:23:00.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Is that salty?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.65,0:23:04.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh boy, you really don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.25,0:23:05.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.53,0:23:07.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I know that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.34,0:23:10.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.59,0:23:12.24,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.26,0:23:16.24,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.24,0:23:17.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.87,0:23:19.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.19,0:23:21.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No one gets angry when they are in an aquarium.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:28.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Their hearts melt when they see the fishes swim happily.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.18,0:23:34.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,All right, what do you say about some ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.64,0:23:36.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! I want one with three balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.82,0:23:40.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I want one as big as a whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.44,0:23:56.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A whale?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.29,0:24:04.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The foamy meringue shines pearl gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.39,0:24:10.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Inside the warm oven a golden life is conceived.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.05,0:24:14.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The warm, sweet taste doesn't bring back memories from childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.84,0:24:17.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to set sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.13,0:24:19.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It would have been better if we had never met.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.07,0:24:23.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't need any memories at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.03,0:24:27.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And then... the journey continues.